{"tid":648604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中財辦官員：不怕貿易戰　「外需佔GDP不到10%」","createTime":"2018-04-30T20:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T04:53:53.000Z","uid":47714,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"23205e25de300472f64c724816034fe0c2bba2f4","tid":648604,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T20:29:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2062948?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2062948%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=W5QmFJY5hwVuk6%2FN%2FfnFXF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5393791b\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2062948?r=mcsdfb2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/MRF44C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FMRF44C&h=ebc95d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美經貿議題的高層級磋商，最快本周內登場。在此前夕，中央財經委員會辦公室副主任楊偉民在公開論壇稱，中國不用怕貿易戰，因為外需佔GDP的比例已不到10%，內需扛得起由中國經濟。<br />\n<br />\n中國經濟思想與實踐研究院和中國經濟50人論壇共同主辦的「2018中國與世界思想對話會」，前天（28日）在清華大學舉行。新浪網今天報道會議部份內容。<br />\n<br />\n清華大學教授李稻葵在會上向中財辦副主任楊偉民問道，「如果短期內爆發了貿易戰，（中國）是不是扛得起」。楊回應稱，「我覺得不怕」。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉民指出，「在中國目前的經濟增長中，內需佔比很大，外需佔比已經不到10%了，大概在6%-7%之間，就是假如說完全沒有進出口，完全停止了，我們去年的增長速度是6%，就足夠了」。"},{"pid":"49094cb6f406846940eeabbd8f52d889c2bc94a1","tid":648604,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T20:30:25.000Z","msg":"立即鎖但"},{"pid":"6030386769a089d87d7713462c7848c111a1c5c8","tid":648604,"uid":24044,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"49094cb6f406846940eeabbd8f52d889c2bc94a1","tid":648604,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T20:30:25.000Z","msg":"立即鎖但"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T20:30:38.000Z","msg":"立即鎖國"},{"pid":"4ddd948c332070f36b9c421ffb823f661212759d","tid":648604,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T20:32:03.000Z","msg":"起樓拆樓起路拆路"},{"pid":"3ab586a922ab9e660b1ac964b8e5baa1dc74e6fb","tid":648604,"uid":36820,"like":0,"